         (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>.)
       </span>
      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d321n1-ptr" id="PJA09d321n1">1</a>
      
   <p>No letter from <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to Wilson containing such a list has been found.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d321n2-ptr" id="PJA09d321n2">2</a>
      
   <p>For the printing of the <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Report</span> in the publications indicated by <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>, see Thomas Digges letter of 14 April, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-09-02-0103&amp;expandNote=PJA09d111n2#PJA09d111n2" class="document">note 2</a> (above).</p>

